    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "This is likely to have been inadvertently fixed with either #7813 or #7993 where we added proper support for unsigned hex and binary literals.\r\n\r\nThese changes are not being backported to PS 5.1 -- almost nothing is able to be backported to the Windows PowerShell edition. I'm closing this as resolved for now, thanks for following up and confirming it's no longer an issue in 7.2+ ðŸ™‚ ",
